description: This Chainlink VRF common Gatinho purrs with a rating of 36, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 72, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Stringalong for East, 2 for South, and 3 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50362-97232-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [72 Votes, Common]
